==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Rouser
<hw>Rous"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One who,
or that which, rouses.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Something very exciting or great.</def>
<mark>[Colloq.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <fld>(Brewing)</fld> <def>A stirrer in a copper for
boiling wort.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Rousing</ent>⟦br⟧
